 not necessary to use the main features of these apps.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-07T10:14:13.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"aviaryan/awesome-no-login-web-apps","categoryHTML":"<h3>Privacy, Security and Cryptography</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://bugmenot.com/\">BugMeNot</a> - A platform for finding and sharing logins of different websites. It helps you find credentials for signing in into different websites.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-07T10:14:13.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"aviaryan/awesome-no-login-web-apps","categoryHTML":"<h3>Programming Editors and IDEs</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.tutorialspoint.com/codingground.htm\">TutorialsPoint Online Tools</a> - Online terminals for Ipython, Octave, Powershell, Redis and lots others. Also has a good collection of IDEs for programming languages.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-07T10:14:13.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"aviaryan/awesome-no-login-web-apps","categoryHTML":"<h3>Programming Editors and IDEs</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://dartpad.dartlang.org/\">DartPad</a> -DartPad is an open-source tool that lets you play with the Dart language in any modern browser.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-07T10:14:13.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"aviaryan/awesome-no-login-web-apps","categoryHTML":"<h3>Search Engines</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://icons8.com/\">icon8</a> - Designers, download the design stuff for free — icons, photos, UX illustrations, and music for your videos.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-07T10:14:13.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"aviaryan/awesome-no-login-web-apps","categoryHTML":"<h3>Study and Education</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.wolframalpha.com\">WolframAlpha</a> - Powerful computational knowledge engine. See <a href=\"https://www.wolframalpha.com/examples/PlottingAndGraphics.html\">plotting graphs examples</a> for help on how to plot graphs.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-11-07T10:14:13.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"phalcon/awesome-phalcon","categoryHTML":"<h2>RESTful</h2>","itemHTML":"<li>